tools.content:
Test Map!


This is the about panel for a test map


Maps can include text in various formats, like:


Bold Italic Underline and strikethrough


Also quote blocks

Ne te quaesiveris extra. - Ralph Waldo Emerson


Also code blocks:

public void someMethod(string someValue)
{
    someValue = "This example sucks";
}


You can add colour to the back or text


And of course, images and video links
